
Server instance:
Load json dats into memory

Page request
Send dat to template, tempalte print out info
Widgets correspond to data types


Front end:
Widgets make ajax get request on change -- json?

Get request handler parses json
finds what object to change
looks for what is changing
updates memory, and serializes to disk


Game server:
monitors json files for changes
if change, dat loader reads & parses the updated json file
feeds this into the updater
